i love him so much i'm so happy
summary: In the video he’s literally standing in front of a void I’m actually crying right now 😭    “Embrace the void and have the...
caption:
In the video he’s literally standing in front of a void I’m actually crying right now 😭

   “Embrace the void and have the courage to exist.“

I’m so glad you’ve found the courage to let yourself exist authentically in the public light. You’re an incredibly inspiring person and I’m so glad to have you in my life, even if that time is only 45 minutes every two years.

Jokes aside, I’m so happy for you. I can’t wait to see where the world takes you. I know you’re going to continue doing amazing things 🖤
